>Description:
When you use Ctrl-E to show the hidden interactions window, the cursor stays in the editor window.  It would be faster to use if hiding the interactions window activated the cursor in the editor window and showing the interactions window activated the cursor in the interactions window.
>How-To-Repeat:
Edit Ctrl-E (hide) Edit Ctrl-E (show) <cursor still in editor>
